title: Hillary Clinton's poise in Benghazi testimony boosts 2016 prospects
text: It's been a good 10 days for Hillary Rodham Clinton. She was widely deemed the winner of the first Democratic debate, chased Jim Webb from the race, headed off her biggest primary threat in Vice President Joseph R. Biden and on Thursday defused the Benghazi time bomb with a performance ... ...
